channel.title: Only I can get on my server?
channel.description:
I can only get on my server when I enter no server or IP... and no one else can get on.
It's meant to be on 89.241.229.40 or joggerscape.no-ip.org... I also have the no-ip program installed and running, as well as port forwarding attempted... and I think I did it.
What's wrong with my server??!
